%description
This is a terminal UI as drop-in replacement for hledger add.

It improves in the following ways on hledger's add command:

* Interactive as-you-type completion for account names and descriptions with
optional fuzzy matching.

* Integrated calculator: Amounts can be written as simple sums with real-time
feedback on the result.

* All actions while entering a transaction can be undone

* Configurable format for date input. Instead of 'y/m/d' it is also possible to
use other formats like the german 'd.m.y'.


